videos.title: Wissahickon Mountain Biking Edit V2 - NEW BIKE!! - FUEL EX 8!!
videos.description:
This is an edit I made with a friend of mine over winter break with my new bike (Trek Fuel EX 8 27.5+). It was a lot of fun and I hope you enjoy. If you want to watch the bloopers and behind the scenes, go to my channel to see that video.

Music: "Mr. Sandman" by the Chordettes
